= 1.2.0 (2024-09-16)

* Do not require load_ldap_library be called before use of valid? (jeremyevans) (#3)

* Explicitly check for null bytes in login and password in valid? (jeremyevans)

= 1.1.0 (2022-07-19)

* Make fallback to net/ldap work if ldap is not installed (jeremyevans)

* Make default servers, use_ssl, and login_format settings apply (jeremyevans)

* Work with newer net/ldap versions that use Net::LDAP::Error for errors (jeremyevans)

* Avoid verbose mode warnings (jeremyevans)

= 1.0.1 (2011-08-03)

* Fix issue where an empty password would be accepted as a valid anonymous bind (jeremyevans)

= 1.0.0 (2006-08-25)

* Initial public release
